text: Desmiphora travassosi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Mendes in 1938. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora travassosi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1938
